{"tid":2160540,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"德福花園兩日錄5成交 2房減68萬作價750萬","createTime":"2020-08-17T04:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T14:58:17.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2918ac94fe34ba69b90351364efd18a8e1f2fe3c","tid":2160540,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:30:54.000Z","msg":"德福花園兩日錄5成交 2房減68萬作價750萬<br />\n12:00 2020/08/17<br />\n<br />\n&quot;德福花園R座中層10室，2房間隔，望開揚景觀，實用面積約494平方呎.....雙方議價後減價68萬元，減幅達8%，以750萬元沽出單位，實用呎價約15,182元......業主於2001年7月以約152.8萬元購入上述單位，是次轉手帳面獲利約597.2萬，升值近4倍。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2726318/%E5%BE%B7%E7%A6%8F%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5%E9%8C%845%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%C2%A02%E6%88%BF%E6%B8%9B68%E8%90%AC%E4%BD%9C%E5%83%B9750%E8%90%AC?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2726318%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%25A6%258F%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%258C%25845%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25C2%25A02%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%25B8%259B68%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%2583%25B9750%25E8%2590%25AC%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=42a22f62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2726318/%E5%BE%B7%E7%A6%8F%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5%E9%8C%845%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%C2%A02%E6%88%BF%E6%B8%9B68%E8%90%AC%E4%BD%9C%E5%83%B9750%E8%90%AC?mtc=60037</a>"},{"pid":"f42f168de2d55c0c7df97f4510724ce785f04f49","tid":2160540,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:34:00.000Z","msg":"糕糕糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09070a8f9bbb99d97b5641e344e22f8bbed99db","tid":2160540,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:56:44.000Z","msg":"Molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"